{"tid":1461444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武定係和理非? 有冇聽過3.5趴規則? 入嚟睇下啦","createTime":"2019-08-13T07:48:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T08:03:59.000Z","uid":270126,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2b3cfdf7e1def1e87ac0c601b1a53582f5d65643","tid":1461444,"uid":270126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:48:06.000Z","msg":"面對政府加重加大的殘暴鎮壓，反抗者應該採取什麼策略？拉高衝突的勇武對抗？還是堅持「和理非」路線？這是困擾反抗者的難題。同樣地，在研究公民不服從（civil disobedience）或公民反抗（civil resistance）的學術界，也有和平與非和平路線的爭議。<br />\n<br />\n目前任教於哈佛大學甘迺迪學院的Erica Chenoweth，就是和平/非暴力（nonviolent）路線最有名的代表之一。她與Belgioioso 在今年8月5日才剛出版了一篇新論文&ldquo;The physics of dissent and the effects of movement momentum&rdquo;，用力學的p=mv（動量等於質量與速度的乘積）來詮釋反抗運動的能量。簡單來說，她們的論點是：反抗運動的能量=參與者人數x每週反抗事件的次數。這聽起來有點廢話，越多人上街頭，而且天天上街頭，反抗能量當然就越大。<br />\n<br />\n不過，她們這項「非暴力公民反抗」的經驗研究（僅局限於1990年到2014年非洲國家）有個有趣的地方，就是再次印證了Chenoweth長期主張的「3.5趴規則」（3.5% Rule）&mdash;<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一旦全國人民有3.5%以上參與反抗運動（上街頭遊行、參與不合作運動等等），這個反抗運動的成功機率將大幅提升。</span></span>如下面截圖所示，如果只有1.5%人民參與反抗運動（以台灣為例，就是35萬人，香港就是11萬人），就算每週搞個180次反抗事件，領導人下台（她們稱為irregular leader exit）的機率是一成都不到。但是，如果是有3.5%人民參與（以台灣為例，就是80萬人，香港是25萬人），同樣是每週180次反抗事件，領導人下台的機率就高達六成。<br />\n<br />\n簡單來說，Chenoweth對反抗運動者的建議是：<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">採取非暴力的抗爭模式，才能吸引更多人（尤其是害怕暴力與衝擊的溫和人士）加入運動（不是臉書貼文而已，而是真正參與），當人數超過了3.5%的門檻，而且反抗的活動遍地開花（示威遊行、不合作運動、干擾運動等等），反抗運動的成功機率會比暴力反抗更高（根據她以前的經驗研究，非暴力反抗與暴力反抗的成功機率是二比一）。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n不過，必須注意的是，Chenoweth的反對者也很多，族繁不及備載，而且<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">她的經驗研究只適用在「主權國家」，不一定能適用在欠缺主權地位的自治區，例如香港。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yWircqB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyWircqB.jpg&h=c07bd92a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n有興趣的朋友可以看看她的這篇最新論文，以及她2013年的TED演講：<br />\n<br />\n1. &quot; The physics of dissent and the effects of movement momentum &quot;（只能線上閱讀）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/s41562-019-0665-8.epdf?author_access_token=I9P3TYuEFNdyBp78-Cm-rdRgN0jAjWel9jnR3ZoTv0PVAlNz10ZKxcpcSymKQypSZ7J_ck59ccS6P6a5K84ZaNDB6lKfMklCHx8YVEePPI_V91PmHmmAyxmxP6Kqa-13SbaWfnmLYc1T0raXG1dOhQ%3D%3D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41562-019-0665-8.epdf%3Fauthor_access_token%3DI9P3TYuEFNdyBp78-Cm-rdRgN0jAjWel9jnR3ZoTv0PVAlNz10ZKxcpcSymKQypSZ7J_ck59ccS6P6a5K84ZaNDB6lKfMklCHx8YVEePPI_V91PmHmmAyxmxP6Kqa-13SbaWfnmLYc1T0raXG1dOhQ%253D%253D&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDbwfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=d5b5be86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/s41562-019-0665-8.epdf?author_access_token=I9P3TYuEFNdyBp78-Cm-rdRgN0jAjWel9jnR3ZoTv0PVAlNz10ZKxcpcSymKQypSZ7J_ck59ccS6P6a5K84ZaNDB6lKfMklCHx8YVEePPI_V91PmHmmAyxmxP6Kqa-13SbaWfnmLYc1T0raXG1dOhQ%3D%3D</a><br />\n<br />\n2. &quot;The success of nonviolent civil resistance&quot;（TED演講）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YJSehRlU34w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYJSehRlU34w&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDbwfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=d904fc64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YJSehRlU34w</a>"},{"pid":"86869fe5a65c6b8d91e59b8a3f2d21ce10682963","tid":1461444,"uid":270126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:49:26.000Z","msg":"去機埸玩啊"},{"pid":"9cc66622b07cd24e8c4111900bb7a948f31e1f12","tid":1461444,"uid":270126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:50:00.000Z","msg":"日日去機埸 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JUyuUEC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJUyuUEC.jpg&h=8829964e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"92244e2cbd05c0be5ea7009854d64dde58caefea","tid":1461444,"uid":165925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:50:10.000Z","msg":"認同 <br />\n<br />\n不過唔好意思 阻阻你<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">部分示威者停止暴力衝擊<br />\n部分黑警察停止濫用武力<br />\n政府作出讓步並不再企硬<br />\n歡迎和理非繼續合法示威</span></span><br />\n<br />\n齊上齊落同時請考慮每個行動既利與弊<br />\n否則恐怕變成文革2.0<br />\n目標稍有雜質 <br />\n大家就骨牌效應集體做偏左<br />\n花你搭車痾屎時間去重溫<br />\n鏗鏘集：文革五十年（上）<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZOqrQnxq0jA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZOqrQnxq0jA&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDbwfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=8e8e9f65\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZOqrQnxq0jA</a><br />\n<br />\n「團結」雖是美德，但亦係雙刃劍<br />\n<br />\nBe water, be considerate, be safe."},{"pid":"09672ef88d5d6eb2fdf99f39586186dd5c286315","tid":1461444,"uid":117332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:50:39.000Z","msg":"咁暴力有咩意義?"},{"pid":"a84dd1f329f37cee68e1a02921a7655850da638d","tid":1461444,"uid":270126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:51:37.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811"},{"pid":"4cf230d9ec773389c1e90cacf0c22740ee816d82","tid":1461444,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:51:54.000Z","msg":"唔係主權既地區示威代價更大<br />\n<br />\n要keep到 3.5% 以上先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01c9e71c1a78b2829e59d0809533635a3dd061f5","tid":1461444,"uid":270126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:52:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oM7vD6Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoM7vD6Z.jpg&h=0decc865&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1e5d6786c857dcba0ddf4de2065d737a8257f8a7","tid":1461444,"uid":45259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:53:27.000Z","msg":"對極權國家要有幾多percent<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53d546716b841b7459ae0961b257ac0b531e76ec","tid":1461444,"uid":270126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:55:13.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811"},{"pid":"645510f3625876ac280bdc0f0daa3a07373e656c","tid":1461444,"uid":270126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e5d6786c857dcba0ddf4de2065d737a8257f8a7","tid":1461444,"uid":45259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:53:27.000Z","msg":"對極權國家要有幾多percent<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:59:02.000Z","msg":"三松閣：武力抗爭也是義務？ 2019/8/11<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】自雨傘運動以降，香港的大型社會抗爭運動愈趨激烈。但基於各種原因，關於抗爭手段的討論，大多仍着眼於和平與非暴力形式的「公民抗命」（principled disobedience）之上。一旦涉及肢體衝突，往往就被大眾譴責為暴力、非理性與不道德。但為何涉及武力的抗爭必然為錯？哲學家Candice Delmas去年的新著A Duty to Resist: When Disobedience Should Be Uncivil，正嘗試打破這種迷思：論證面對不公義的政制和法律，公民抗命不應限於和平一途，武力抗爭同樣是合理而正當的手段，更是市民的政治責任！下文將介紹其想法，為公民抗命提出和理非以外的理據，供大家思考當下香港抗爭運動的走向。<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】自雨傘運動以降，香港的大型社會抗爭運動愈趨激烈。但基於各種原因，關於抗爭手段的討論，大多仍着眼於和平與非暴力形式的「公民抗命」（principled disobedience）之上。一旦涉及肢體衝突，往往就被大眾譴責為暴力、非理性與不道德。但為何涉及武力的抗爭必然為錯？哲學家Candice Delmas去年的新著A Duty to Resist: When Disobedience Should Be Uncivil，正嘗試打破這種迷思：論證面對不公義的政制和法律，公民抗命不應限於和平一途，武力抗爭同樣是合理而正當的手段，更是市民的政治責任！下文將介紹其想法，為公民抗命提出和理非以外的理據，供大家思考當下香港抗爭運動的走向。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%E5%89%AF%E5%88%8A/article/20190811/s00005/1565460639017/%E4%B8%89%E6%9D%BE%E9%96%A3-%E6%AD%A6%E5%8A%9B%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E4%B9%9F%E6%98%AF%E7%BE%A9%E5%8B%99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E5%2589%25AF%25E5%2588%258A%2Farticle%2F20190811%2Fs00005%2F1565460639017%2F%25E4%25B8%2589%25E6%259D%25BE%25E9%2596%25A3-%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E5%258A%259B%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25E4%25B9%259F%25E6%2598%25AF%25E7%25BE%25A9%25E5%258B%2599&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDbwfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=dda1d627\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E5%2589%25AF%25E5%2588%258A%2Farticle%2F20190811%2Fs00005%2F1565460639017%2F%25E4%25B8%2589%25E6%259D%25BE%25E9%2596%25A3-%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E5%258A%259B%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25E4%25B9%259F%25E6%2598%25AF%25E7%25BE%25A9%25E5%258B%2599&h=14479feb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%E5%89%AF%E5%88%8A/article/20190811/s00005/1565460639017/%E4%B8%89%E6%9D%BE%E9%96%A3-%E6%AD%A6%E5%8A%9B%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E4%B9%9F%E6%98%AF%E7%BE%A9%E5%8B%99</a>"},{"pid":"02485d443dc03abe82d46b0cbdf588ddb6dad51e","tid":1461444,"uid":270126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:00:09.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811"},{"pid":"701a71ea432ac35b9055c991a6f7c47c58eada29","tid":1461444,"uid":270126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:00:24.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811<br />\n香港恐襲"},{"pid":"ed14b9468e63ca4beb3a43e33aacfb9cedcf9b73","tid":1461444,"uid":270126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:01:45.000Z","msg":"真心 可以諗下用咩方式做到3.5%<br />\n例如會唔會係多啲打工仔都可以參與嘅罷買"},{"pid":"3b0a65773a115b6c8d808bf12769c099f48e286a","tid":1461444,"uid":270126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:03:46.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811"},{"pid":"127289274e28a1ddf9f3c4759686e8f77125d34f","tid":1461444,"uid":270126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:03:59.000Z","msg":"日日去機埸"}]}